06:22.484 --> 06:23.786
Not my problem.

06:23.787 --> 06:26.157
I swear that Russian is up to no good.

06:26.158 --> 06:27.459
- What did she do now?
- What?

06:27.460 --> 06:29.063
Not Svetlana. Her father.

06:29.064 --> 06:30.365
You got two weeks.

06:30.366 --> 06:31.802
