11:02.511 --> 11:04.479
Morning, Sergeant. Ready
to hit the shooting range?

11:04.480 --> 11:05.983
Yep. Let me grab my gun.

11:05.984 --> 11:08.087
Okay. What's going on?

11:08.088 --> 11:10.759
