all the anti-shelter signs?

12:33.091 --> 12:35.729
Uh, no idea. Neighbors, probably.

12:35.730 --> 12:37.365
- Not you?
- No.

12:37.366 --> 12:39.904
Good. I was winding up
for a big old tantrum.

12:39.905 --> 12:41.875
I'm so fucking sick of these phonies

12:41.876 --> 12:43.444
talking like they give a shit.

12:43.445 --> 12:45.949
