"Ew. Homeless people."

12:45.950 --> 12:47.118
You live around here?

12:47.119 --> 12:48.320
I work on Cermak.

12:48.321 --> 12:50.024
You know Children of the Night?

12:50.025 --> 12:51.493
It's a center for at-risk youth.

12:51.494 --> 12:53.197
Some of those kids
have no place to live,

12:53.198 --> 12:55.201
so I'm the mouthy asshole
who tries to place them.

12:55.202 --> 12:57.105
- Trevor.
- Ian.

12:57.106 --> 12:59.177
Uh, which one's the shelter?

13:01.549 --> 13:03.117
Thanks. I'll check it out.

13:03.118 --> 13:04.854
Nice charm.

13:04.855 --> 13:06.925
(INDIE ROCK MUSIC)

13:06.926 --> 13:08.895
You up all night saving lives?

13:08.896 --> 13:10.966
